column5: Has anyone ever heard of this lake, it is north of lake kabinakagami, Ive heard theres one lodge on the lake, but cant find any info.

The Cameron Lake that I am aware of is an Outpost lake east ofKakagi(Crow Lake) just North of Nestor Falls, Ontario.This is an Outpost Lake that has no resort on it but has an outpost cabin run by Allens Crow Lake Lodge, Nestor Falls.
